{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"unref"},{"text":"()","kind":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Once the reference count reaches zero, the directory will be closed and all"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"resources associated with it will be freed. If [method"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GLib.Dir.close"},{"type":"text","text":"] is"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"called when the reference count is greater than zero, the directory is closed","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"but the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GDir"},{"type":"text","text":" structure will not be freed until its reference count reaches"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"zero.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"It is an error to call any of the "},{"code":"GDir","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" methods other than"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"[method","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GLib.Dir.ref"},{"type":"text","text":"] and [method"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GLib.Dir.unref"},{"text":"] on a ","type":"text"},{"code":"GDir","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" after calling","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"[method","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GLib.Dir.close"},{"type":"text","text":"] on it."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/glib\/dir\/unref()"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib","doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/Dir","doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/Dir\/DirProtocol-Implementations"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/Dir\/un